              <span className="text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full" style={{ backgroundColor: "#FFF8DC", color: "#7B5E00" }}>✨ Fresh, Made to Order</span>
            </div>
            <h1 className="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.4rem] font-bold text-foreground leading-[1.1] mb-5" style={{ fontFamily: "'Playfair Display', serif" }}>
              The Taste of <span style={{ color: "#1B4332" }}>Aajobaanche</span> Gharche Fare
            </h1>
            <p className="text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-md leading-relaxed">
              Authentic Maharashtrian faral, jaggery ladoos and festive sweets, handcrafted in Magarpatta City, Pune since 2015. No preservatives. No shortcuts.
            </p>
